Welcome to help 
 
TODO: Embed help menu. Add bot to LAH official discord. Get rich presence. 
Two functionalities: Emojis and Store Tags 
***Commands(num params):***
settoken: settoken(2) WHEREIN the first word is the tag "token", the other words are the "key"
gettoken: gettoken(1) WHEREIN you input the token name and the bot will return the key
allemotes: allemotes(0) WHEREIN every single emote on the current server is listed
emote: emote(1) WHEREIN the emote name you type out is searched. if found, added as reaction
help: help(0) WHEREIN you get a help menu
ayy: ayy(0) WHEREIN it returns the best emote response amirite
